). In more recent times it was famous as the name of the actress  Grace Kelly  (  1928–82 ), who became  Princess Grace  of Monaco. In Ireland it is used as an Anglicized form of   Gráinne   ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Grace Pinchbeck was born in 1457, in Pinchbeck, Lincolnshire, England, United Kingdom, her father, John Pinchbeck, was 26 and her mother, Kathrine Sarsonne, was 23. She married John Brown Jr before 1471, in England. They were the parents of at least 1 son. She died in 1495, in Stamford, Lincolnshire, England, United Kingdom, at the age of 38, and was buried in Stamford, Lincolnshire, England."},"et":{"1457–1495":"1457–1495","1457–Male":"1457–Surnud","1450–Male":"1450–Surnud","1476–1550":"1476–1550","1470–1506":"1470–1506","1431–1457":"1431–1457","1434–Female":"1434–Surnud","1495":"1495","1550":"1550","1483":"umbes 1483","1450":"1450","1470":"1470","1457":"1457","1434":"1434","1476":"1476","1454":"1454","1431":"1431","1474":"1474","before 1471":"enne 1471","1506":"1506","Surrey, England, United Kingdom":"Surrey, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Stamford, Lincolnshire, England, United Kingdom":"Stamford, Lincolnshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Tolethorpe, Rutland, England":"Rutland, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Stamford, Lincolnshire, England":"Stamford, Lincolnshire, England","England":"England","Pinchbeck, Lincolnshire, England":"Pinchbeck, Lincolnshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","England, United Kingdom":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1457–1495":"1457–1495","1457–Male":"1457–Kuollut","1450–Male":"1450–Kuollut","1476–1550":"1476–1550","1470–1506":"1470–1506","1431–1457":"1431–1457","1434–Female":"1434–Kuollut","1495":"1495","1550":"1550","1483":"noin 1483","1450":"1450","1470":"1470","1457":"1457","1434":"1434","1476":"1476","1454":"1454","1431":"1431","1474":"1474","before 1471":"ennen vuotta 1471","1506":"1506","Surrey, England, United Kingdom":"Surrey, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Stamford, Lincolnshire, England, United Kingdo